modShortDescription: Weed Whacker mod is great for clearing large swathes of plants from the ground.
modDescription:
This is available right out of the gate, the catch is you need to fight the required materials and a workbench. Weed Whacker mod is great for clearing large swathes of plants from the ground.

**[Download](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1r4XNfkSJQJ1qBoyMshG7W0eBNVfcWKbW/view?usp=sharing)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/21494-alucards-modlets/).
